Show all packages:
adb shell pm list packages

Show disabled packages:
adb shell pm list packages -d

Disable package:
adb shell pm disable-user --user 0 <package_to_disable>

Enable package:
adb shell pm enable <package_to_enable>

Uninstall package for user:
adb shell pm uninstall -k --user 0 com.google.android.gm

Reinstall package which was uninstalled for user:
adb shell cmd package install-existing com.miui.bugreport

Uninstall package completely:
adb uninstall com.miui.bugreport

